                        Plus d’informations sur Google Analytics : https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites?hl=fr
                    </p>
                    <p class="cgu mt-sm-4 mt-3">Consentement :</p>
                    <p class="cgu mt-sm-4 mt-3">
